[[File:Thunderbolts* Trailer 10.png|{{AltFloat}}|Walker ignores his crying son]]
{{Quote|If you don't like the way that I do it, then you can do it yourself, okay?|John Walker to [[Olivia Walker]]|Thunderbolts*}}
